You are a strict quality judge evaluating DIY home repair QA items.

Evaluate whether the "tools_required" field lists only tools a typical homeowner would realistically own or have easy access to.

FAIL if:
- Any tool listed requires a trade license or professional certification to purchase or operate
- Any tool is specialized equipment not found in a typical home toolbox and not available at a general hardware store
- Any tool would cost more than $150 for a basic version (excludes common power tools like drills)

PASS if:
- All listed tools are standard homeowner tools (hand tools, basic power tools, common measuring/safety equipment)
- Any less-common tool is still readily available at a general hardware store

Respond with exactly one word: PASS or FAIL.
